venue.name: Todd Morsilli Clay Court Tennis Center, ROGER WILLIAMS PARK

item.description:
We have begun to offer our Flexible SPOT GAME MATCHING SERVICES.

If you want to play a match - need a partner / opponent, then sign up for a match with SPOT.

All matches are slated for 2 hour time slots and include a new can of balls.  $10 for doubles matches.

Fees are waived for SPOT pass holders but they must supply the new can of balls for their court.

Please  your skill level so I can be sure to match you up with players of similar levels of experience.

Also if you sign up, you MUST show up!  There will be 3 other players counting on your attendance.
item.how_to_find_us: next to zoo in Roger Williams Park or enter 100 Hawthorne St Providence, RI 02907 in GPS.
item.name: Mixed/Men's /Women's Doubles
